# Cursor Rules for Broky Project

## MongoDB Commands
```bash
python test_mongo.py                                    # Test connection
python scripts/mongo_query.py list                      # List collections
python scripts/mongo_query.py query -c users            # Query all
python scripts/mongo_query.py query -c users -f '{}'    # Query with filter
python scripts/mongo_query.py insert -c users -d '{}'   # Insert document
```

## Database Usage
```python
from src.app.core.database import get_db
db = get_db()
collection = db['collection_name']
```

## Project Context
Broky: WhatsApp real estate assistant (FastAPI + MongoDB + Infobip + Whisper)

